#: ../../../source/docs/porting/connecting_cpp_and_javascript/WebIDL-Binder.rst:280
msgid "Un-deletable classes (NoDelete)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/porting/connecting_cpp_and_javascript/WebIDL-Binder.rst:282
msgid ""
"If a class cannot be deleted (because the destructor is private), specify "
"``[NoDelete]`` in the IDL file."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/porting/connecting_cpp_and_javascript/WebIDL-Binder.rst:294
